java.lang.Object

mb.pso.issuesystem.service.impl.im.SuppressedChatService
All Implemented Interfaces:
CrudService<SuppressedChat,Integer>
@Service public class SuppressedChatService extends AbstractCrudService<SuppressedChat,Integer>
Service for managing suppressed chats. Handles suppressing and unsuppressing chats for specific employees.

      public void suppressChat(Integer chatId, Employee employee)

      employee - the Employee for whom the chat is being suppressed
